title: Qaleh Kohneh, Saqqez
text: Qaleh Kohneh (, also <a href="Romanize">Romanize</a>d as Qal’eh Kohneh and Qal‘eh-ye Kohneh) is a village in <a href="Saheb%20Rural%20District">Saheb Rural District</a>, <a href="Ziviyeh%20District">Ziviyeh District</a>, <a href="Saqqez%20County">Saqqez County</a>, <a href="Kurdistan%20Province">Kurdistan Province</a>, Iran. At the 2006 census, its population was 546, in 109 families. The village is populated by <a href="Kurds">Kurds</a>.
